# Summary and Keywords

The documentation describes how to integrate Amplitude with Hotjar using a destination plugin that forwards Amplitude events to Hotjar's tracking system. It provides code examples for creating a custom HotjarPlugin class that implements the DestinationPlugin interface and demonstrates how to initialize and use this plugin with Amplitude's browser SDK.

